WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:03.850
I found a long, blonde
hair on Simon's scarf.

00:03.900 --> 00:06.670
You followed me? What did
you think I was doing?

00:06.720 --> 00:10.130
I'm pretty sure my husband
is sleeping with someone else.

00:10.180 --> 00:12.690
I'd be nothing without her. She's...

00:12.740 --> 00:14.850
a wonderful mother,

00:14.900 --> 00:16.090
a talented doctor

00:16.140 --> 00:18.540
and not a bad little earner!

00:19.260 --> 00:20.800
GEMMA GASPS

00:22.380 --> 00:26.090
So in sympathy and admiration,

00:26.140 --> 00:28.610
please be upstanding for a toast to Gemma.

00:28.660 --> 00:30.580
ALL: To Gemma!

00:32.420 --> 00:33.970
'Heaven has no rage

00:34.020 --> 00:36.560
'like love to hatred turned...

00:37.180 --> 00:39.570
'Nor hell have a fury

00:39.620 --> 00:41.900
'like the woman scorned.'

